{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>心理測驗｜日本人氣綜藝節目《月曜夜未央》曾經在節目尾聲，為觀眾送上一個號稱超準的顏色心理測驗，簡單一步就可以了解你內心的慾望和渴求的事物。</p><p>👉follow 好食玩飛ig ✈️免費睇旅遊飲食攻略</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200804/367385778273259520.jpeg/CJhaYzgMOifgI-ASWBIaOezSuj-gavhqwZ6d7MGenew\" alt=\"主持人松子原本仍是半信半疑，結果一公佈後卻大呼超準，連他也嚇一跳！（圖片來源：《月曜夜未央》）\"><figcaption>主持人松子原本仍是半信半疑，結果一公佈後卻大呼超準，連他也嚇一跳！（圖片來源：《月曜夜未央》）</figcaption></figure><p>這個顏色心理測驗據說是根據沖繩一直沿用至今的「琉球風水」，只要在以下8個顏色裡憑直覺挑選自己最在意的顏色，即可了解內心慾望和渴求的事物。</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200807/368444861910749184.png/gpNSipSEq2asLlYVawQB5EBSDWFLDSysK4BpDSuAaQ0\"><p>決定好就可以按下圖看結果👇👇👇</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367645041944039424.jpeg/tTN0lAzWL0CbGesBLhoFpXT2NdzMQyNu56kwx-epMMc\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367645133111431168.jpeg/mt0TPko28GFnv9MSuxjoGB5P_vmKYf95gdH2-IHR9vg\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632584756301824.jpeg/hFdNDPXtK43LdJHTF7l4ewvA7bRygrDw-z7Ek_s-xJM\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632586857648128.jpeg/Bz9LlMnPKv2huy7JiUebZoD0rblH6aR8zoG7KM6Buyg\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632588782833664.jpeg/u43PDUAgbPbzR1ObrQR_5WJPqEs4Awqxb_Ud2W_1Hdk\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632590540247040.jpeg/6zQt57bqgSqWoE72kIOzWLtzbznKUuknSS5bC0kuWws\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632592301854720.jpeg/aJSaEcxOcgPqtBYWM2AJ-5yglrYlw7BOxjC4n8YwuJ8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632594277371904.jpeg/_aXtnVS8_hrPv74MtCiTMz9CAAZjT5NhyGgSs8hoErM\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632596332580864.jpeg/rMumNEmbGcVQ6-aJ9RBbwM042QjsWJrLIcddhiHHXYY\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632597943193600.jpeg/9HWPk-8oN-5ar5cU8kJd11Ol9TcUzCfJNl0uIDZdLiA\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632534202355712.jpeg/_GGh-PWXSFYvI9gcbh4iRY_XRD-GexXrGFVz0RhVc9E\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632536307896320.jpeg/2Ze749guPu_GTwAjucP248Jtq0pDrR4yBPjIVAT4yFQ\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632538606374912.jpeg/tIhrj51tcpIqRAIFCdKkongS2N_Yf76wf5rj7n-a4-4\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632541370421248.jpeg/3aBR6z2YOVrABmaaxSn2CL7ijTNmKu6Mby4n8m8uJ_I\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632544268685312.jpeg/u7-zJALyIKpm1QoqAppkqmUb46XRC6fq3gyw394MsN8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200805/367632546537803776.jpeg/osUxTzPh3CPHWWvzBd9k2RBbuwB2wnb6pKAg4qSgIOI\"><p>不知大家又覺得準唔準呢，歡迎留言與我們分享！</p><p>同場加映：6款耳仔形狀測潛藏真實性格</p><p>日本YouTube頻道「幸せ＊Style」日前分享一個心理測驗，只要根據自己的耳朵形狀即可了解可能連自己也沒有發覺的隱藏性格！首先檢視一下自己的耳朵是屬於以下哪一款，如果看不清楚可以請身邊的朋友或家人幫幫忙！👇👇👇</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200730/365514333037400064.jpeg/QAYYCkxD_aQbAA6wpEAOW0YezT-gCyjBUx_J11Mfydc\"><p>決定好就可以看結果：日本熱傳耳仔形狀測真實性格　耳垂大小有分別、精靈耳是藝術家？</p><p>（全文完）👉follow 好食玩飛ig ✈️免費睇旅遊飲食攻略</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-04T04:05:20.885983+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":452,"images":19,"source":"HK01 熱話","fallback":"none"}}